#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Hypergeometric distribution."
msgstr "从超几何分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a hypergeometric distribution with specified "
"parameters, ngood (ways to make a good selection), nbad (ways to make a "
"bad selection), and nsample = number of items sampled, which is less than"
" or equal to the sum ngood + nbad."
msgstr ""
"样本从具有指定参数的超几何分布中抽取，参数包括 ngood（做出好选择的方式数"
"）、nbad（做出坏选择的方式数）和 nsample（抽取的项目数），其中 nsample "
"小于或等于 ngood + nbad 的总和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:8 of
msgid "Number of ways to make a good selection.  Must be nonnegative."
msgstr "做出好选择的方式数。必须为非负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:10 of
msgid "Number of ways to make a bad selection.  Must be nonnegative."
msgstr "做出坏选择的方式数。必须为非负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:12 of
msgid "Number of items sampled.  Must be at least 1 and at most ``ngood + nbad``."
msgstr "抽取的项目数。必须至少为 1 且至多为 ``ngood + nbad``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:15 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``ngood``, ``nbad``, and ``nsample`` are all scalars.  "
"Otherwise, ``np.broadcast(ngood, nbad, nsample).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``ngood``、``nbad`` 和 ``nsample`` 均为"
"标量，则返回单个值。否则抽取 ``np.broadcast(ngood, nbad, nsample).size`` "
"个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:21 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上的期望块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:23 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:25 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:28 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized hypergeometric "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的超几何分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.hypergeom`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:34 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布函数或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:37 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:38 of
msgid "The probability density for the Hypergeometric distribution is"
msgstr "超几何分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:40 of
msgid ""
"P(x) = \\frac{\\binom{m}{n}\\binom{N-m}{n-x}}{\\binom{N}{n}},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:42 of
msgid "where :math:`0 \\le x \\le m` and :math:`n+m-N \\le x \\le n`"
msgstr "其中 :math:`0 \\le x \\le m` 且 :math:`n+m-N \\le x \\le n`"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:44 of
msgid ""
"for P(x) the probability of x successes, n = ngood, m = nbad, and N = "
"number of samples."
msgstr "对于 P(x)，x 表示成功的次数，n = ngood，m = nbad，N = 样本数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:47 of
msgid ""
"Consider an urn with black and white marbles in it, ngood of them black "
"and nbad are white. If you draw nsample balls without replacement, then "
"the hypergeometric distribution describes the distribution of black balls"
" in the drawn sample."
msgstr ""
"考虑一个装有黑色和白色弹珠的罐子，其中 ngood 个为黑色，nbad 个为白色。"
"如果在不放回的情况下抽取 nsample 个球，则超几何分布描述了抽样样本中黑球的"
"分布情况。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:52 of
msgid ""
"Note that this distribution is very similar to the binomial distribution,"
" except that in this case, samples are drawn without replacement, whereas"
" in the Binomial case samples are drawn with replacement (or the sample "
"space is infinite). As the sample space becomes large, this distribution "
"approaches the binomial."
msgstr ""
"注意，该分布与二项分布非常相似，不同之处在于此时样本是不放回抽取的，而在"
"二项分布中样本是放回抽取的（或者样本空间是无限的）。当样本空间变大时，该"
"分布趋近于二项分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:59 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:60 of
msgid ""
"Lentner, Marvin, \"Elementary Applied Statistics\", Bogden and Quigley, "
"1972."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:62 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Hypergeometric Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A "
"Wolfram Web Resource. "
"http://mathworld.wolfram.com/HypergeometricDistribution.html"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:65 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Hypergeometric distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypergeometric_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:69 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:70 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.hypergeometric.hypergeometric:80 of
msgid ""
"Suppose you have an urn with 15 white and 15 black marbles. If you pull "
"15 marbles at random, how likely is it that 12 or more of them are one "
"color?"
msgstr ""
"假设你有一个装有15个白色和15个黑色弹珠的瓮。如果你随机抽取15个弹珠，其中"
"12个或更多弹珠是同一种颜色的概率是多少？"

